/wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Total Business</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Total Business is a powerful multi-purpose WordPress theme for businesses. It is specially designed for a wood factory, plastic factory, steel factory, metal factory, a furniture company, creative agency, web designer, graphic designer, photographer.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/total-business-multipurpose-business-wp-theme/12838026" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Total Business</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Simplify</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Simplify is a good solution for Smart Small Business Companies and Organizations.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://d5creation.com/theme/simplify/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Simplify</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Listable</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Listable is a listing directory WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/listable-a-friendly-directory-wordpress-theme/13398377" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Listable</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Travelista</h2>\n<blockquote><p>A premium blog style responsive WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: cent