(1771, 1, '2016-09-30 16:48:43', '2016-09-30 16:48:43', '<div id="item-120751-1" class="item item-1 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap">\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h1>NEWGEN SS17</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>FASHION FLASH CARDS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven up-and-coming fashion designers, ten quick-fire questions, one introduction to the NEWGEN class of SS17.\r\n\r\nNot heard of NEWGEN? Here’s the lowdown: NEWGEN is a Topshop-sponsored initiative, that nurtures fashion’s most exciting emerging\r\ntalent and gives them the opportunity to show their latest collections on-schedule at London Fashion Week. Get to know this season’s\r\ndesigners via their fashion flash cards below.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-2" class="item item-2 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK-2.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Sadie Williams - 2" usemap="#imgmap201691111631" width="1200" height="754" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201691111631" name="imgmap201691111631"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Sadie Williams - 2" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>SADIE WILLIAMS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLadbroke Grove, London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHaggerston, by the canal\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAbsolute ’90s has been on\r\nway too much, and\r\nBeyoncé’s Lemonade.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WEARS YOUR CLOTHES?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLots of my friends buy them\r\nto wear on nights out, like a\r\nSadie Williams girl band.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMy good friend Poppy Kane.\r\nShe styles my shows and I\r\nlove to see how she works,\r\nshe’s a cool girl.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI’ve been looking at signal\r\ncodes and flags, there’s a bit of a nautical theme - they’re\r\nquite abstract and graphic and I like that.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SNACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nWe’re trying to be healthy, so\r\nfruit, but it’s mostly Haribo\r\nbefore fashion week.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nTactile, graphic, playful,\r\nfeminine, sporty and\r\na bit sparkly.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHAT WAS YOUR BIG BREAK?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBesides being able to do this\r\nin the first place! This year I\r\nwas on Forbes 30 under 30\r\nlist for the arts, too.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"LOTS OF MY FRIENDS BUY THEM TO\r\nWEAR ON NIGHTS OUT, LIKE A SADIE\r\nWILLIAMS GIRL BAND."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-3" class="item item-3 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK3.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 - Molly Goddard 3 " usemap="#imgmap201691145438" width="1200" height="769" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201691145438" name="imgmap201691145438"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 - Molly Goddard 3 " shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>MOLLY GODDARD</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nWest London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLadbroke Grove, West London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBaby kangaroos, I keep seeing photos of them everywhere!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRavers. I’ve been looking at a Lewisham library that got squatted in and turned into a rave as inspiration. It’s the idea of living for the weekend.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMiuccia Prada.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMy sister, I think she’s really cool. And Tim Walker.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDesert Island Discs, you get to listen to music and learn things at the same time!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nTulle or smocking.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAt the end of my show last season all the models started dancing, they weren’t supposed to but it was so great, they went wild.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"BABY KANGAROOS, I KEEP SEEING\r\nPHOTOS OF THEM EVERYWHERE! "</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-4" class="item item-4 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK4.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Ryan Lo - 4" usemap="#imgmap201696131211" width="1200" height="769" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696131211" name="imgmap201696131211"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Ryan Lo - 4" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>RYAN LO</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHong Kong\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRight now I’m listening to\r\nMozart, but I did have Celine\r\nDion on for the entire week\r\nlast week - she’s making a\r\nfashion comeback!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBethnal Green\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nCasual, but designer casual.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nFree time! And happiness.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Middle East, basically\r\nSex and The City 2 when\r\nthey go to Abu Dhabi.\r\nIt’s a bit Disney, a bit\r\nArabian Nights.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Ryan Lo woman and I\r\nare very different. I’m quite\r\ncasual but my muse is\r\nmore put-together and\r\nover-accessorised,\r\nlike a princess.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSJP, duh! I need a\r\nnew muse…\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHAT WAS YOUR BIG BREAK?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI think I’m having my big\r\nbreak right now, it’s my last\r\nseason with NEWGEN so I’m\r\nmaking the most of it.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"...I DID HAVE CELINE DION ON FOR\r\nTHE ENTIRE WEEK LAST WEEK - SHE’S\r\nMAKING A FASHION COMEBACK!"</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-5" class="item item-5 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK5.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Marta Jakubowki - 5" usemap="#imgmap20169614149" width="1200" height="777" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap20169614149" name="imgmap20169614149"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Marta Jakubowki - 5" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nPoland, then Germany\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nIt’s always people I\r\nappreciate for their work and\r\naesthetic, Corinne Day and\r\nMarina Abramovic are on my\r\nmoodboards every season.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAn easy dress and converse.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven Sisters\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSleep! And Meditation, I’ve\r\njust been in India.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRed, white and black!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nFunerals, the celebration of\r\ndeath. I went to Varanasi in\r\nIndia - where they burn\r\nbodies on the river Ganges\r\n- it was amazing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMeeting Rei Kawakubo in\r\nParis, I love her and she\r\ntold me she really\r\nappreciated my work!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSilence, I need it to concentrate.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"CORINNE DAY AND MARINA\r\nABRAMOVIC ARE ON MY\r\nMOODBOARDS EVERY SEASON.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>MARTA JAKUBOWSKI</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-6" class="item item-6 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK6.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Faustine Steinmetz - 6" usemap="#imgmap201696144027" width="1200" height="763" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696144027" name="imgmap201696144027"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Faustine Steinmetz - 6" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SNACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>FAUSTINE STEINMETZ</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nParis, but I think of London\r\nas my home too.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven Sisters\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHummus and carrots but\r\nnormally I have crisps for\r\ndinner every night in the\r\nlead up to fashion week.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nA massive black sweatshirt\r\ndress, I’ve been wearing\r\nit every day for the last\r\ntwo years.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe light, which is very\r\nabstract and different for\r\nme. Think shadows, light and\r\nhow colour looks in different\r\ntypes of light.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDenim, but slightly twisted\r\nin a weird way.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDefinitely Charlotte\r\nRampling. She’s so confident\r\nand I think that’s the sexiest\r\nthing about a woman.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI got introduced to Karl\r\nLagerfeld and he already\r\nknew who I was, I couldn’t\r\nspeak for ages and then I\r\nhad to go and call my mum!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Dazed playlist.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"DENIM, BUT SLIGHTLY TWISTED\r\nIN A WEIRD WAY."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-7" class="item item-7 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK7.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Ashley Williams - 7" usemap="#imgmap201696145953" width="1200" height="771" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696145953" name="imgmap201696145953"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Ashley Williams - 7" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WEARS IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSharjah, United Arab Emirates\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHackney\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBras.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nGirls and boys everywhere.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSofia Coppola.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nE.T\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\n‘R U Married?’ by Detroit\r\nin Effect.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nA teenage boy designing for\r\ngirls, with lots of graphics.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAll of it!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>ASHLEY WILLIAMS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"A TEENAGE BOY DESIGNING FOR\r\nGIRLS, WITH LOTS OF GRAPHICS."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-8" class="item item-8 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK-8.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Paula Knorr - 8" usemap="#imgmap201696153743" width="1200" height="852" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696153743" name="imgmap201696153743"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Paula Knorr - 8" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 "></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'NEWGEN SS17  FASHION FLASH CARDS', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'newgen-ss17-fashion-flash-cards__trashed', '', '', '2016-09-30 16:49:48', '2016-09-30 16:49:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/madlips/?p=1771', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1772, 1, '2016-09-30 16:48:43', '2016-09-30 16:48:43', '<div id="item-120751-1" class="item item-1 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap">\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h1>NEWGEN SS17</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>FASHION FLASH CARDS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven up-and-coming fashion designers, ten quick-fire questions, one introduction to the NEWGEN class of SS17.\r\n\r\nNot heard of NEWGEN? Here’s the lowdown: NEWGEN is a Topshop-sponsored initiative, that nurtures fashion’s most exciting emerging\r\ntalent and gives them the opportunity to show their latest collections on-schedule at London Fashion Week. Get to know this season’s\r\ndesigners via their fashion flash cards below.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-2" class="item item-2 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK-2.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Sadie Williams - 2" usemap="#imgmap201691111631" width="1200" height="754" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201691111631" name="imgmap201691111631"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Sadie Williams - 2" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>SADIE WILLIAMS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLadbroke Grove, London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHaggerston, by the canal\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAbsolute ’90s has been on\r\nway too much, and\r\nBeyoncé’s Lemonade.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WEARS YOUR CLOTHES?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLots of my friends buy them\r\nto wear on nights out, like a\r\nSadie Williams girl band.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMy good friend Poppy Kane.\r\nShe styles my shows and I\r\nlove to see how she works,\r\nshe’s a cool girl.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI’ve been looking at signal\r\ncodes and flags, there’s a bit of a nautical theme - they’re\r\nquite abstract and graphic and I like that.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SNACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nWe’re trying to be healthy, so\r\nfruit, but it’s mostly Haribo\r\nbefore fashion week.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nTactile, graphic, playful,\r\nfeminine, sporty and\r\na bit sparkly.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHAT WAS YOUR BIG BREAK?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBesides being able to do this\r\nin the first place! This year I\r\nwas on Forbes 30 under 30\r\nlist for the arts, too.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"LOTS OF MY FRIENDS BUY THEM TO\r\nWEAR ON NIGHTS OUT, LIKE A SADIE\r\nWILLIAMS GIRL BAND."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-3" class="item item-3 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK3.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 - Molly Goddard 3 " usemap="#imgmap201691145438" width="1200" height="769" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201691145438" name="imgmap201691145438"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 - Molly Goddard 3 " shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>MOLLY GODDARD</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nWest London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nLadbroke Grove, West London\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBaby kangaroos, I keep seeing photos of them everywhere!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRavers. I’ve been looking at a Lewisham library that got squatted in and turned into a rave as inspiration. It’s the idea of living for the weekend.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMiuccia Prada.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMy sister, I think she’s really cool. And Tim Walker.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDesert Island Discs, you get to listen to music and learn things at the same time!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nTulle or smocking.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAt the end of my show last season all the models started dancing, they weren’t supposed to but it was so great, they went wild.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"BABY KANGAROOS, I KEEP SEEING\r\nPHOTOS OF THEM EVERYWHERE! "</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-4" class="item item-4 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK4.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Ryan Lo - 4" usemap="#imgmap201696131211" width="1200" height="769" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696131211" name="imgmap201696131211"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Ryan Lo - 4" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>RYAN LO</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHong Kong\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRight now I’m listening to\r\nMozart, but I did have Celine\r\nDion on for the entire week\r\nlast week - she’s making a\r\nfashion comeback!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBethnal Green\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nCasual, but designer casual.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nFree time! And happiness.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Middle East, basically\r\nSex and The City 2 when\r\nthey go to Abu Dhabi.\r\nIt’s a bit Disney, a bit\r\nArabian Nights.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Ryan Lo woman and I\r\nare very different. I’m quite\r\ncasual but my muse is\r\nmore put-together and\r\nover-accessorised,\r\nlike a princess.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSJP, duh! I need a\r\nnew muse…\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHAT WAS YOUR BIG BREAK?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI think I’m having my big\r\nbreak right now, it’s my last\r\nseason with NEWGEN so I’m\r\nmaking the most of it.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"...I DID HAVE CELINE DION ON FOR\r\nTHE ENTIRE WEEK LAST WEEK - SHE’S\r\nMAKING A FASHION COMEBACK!"</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-5" class="item item-5 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK5.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Marta Jakubowki - 5" usemap="#imgmap20169614149" width="1200" height="777" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap20169614149" name="imgmap20169614149"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Marta Jakubowki - 5" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nPoland, then Germany\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nIt’s always people I\r\nappreciate for their work and\r\naesthetic, Corinne Day and\r\nMarina Abramovic are on my\r\nmoodboards every season.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAn easy dress and converse.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven Sisters\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSleep! And Meditation, I’ve\r\njust been in India.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nRed, white and black!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nFunerals, the celebration of\r\ndeath. I went to Varanasi in\r\nIndia - where they burn\r\nbodies on the river Ganges\r\n- it was amazing.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nMeeting Rei Kawakubo in\r\nParis, I love her and she\r\ntold me she really\r\nappreciated my work!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSilence, I need it to concentrate.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"CORINNE DAY AND MARINA\r\nABRAMOVIC ARE ON MY\r\nMOODBOARDS EVERY SEASON.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>MARTA JAKUBOWSKI</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-6" class="item item-6 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK6.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Faustine Steinmetz - 6" usemap="#imgmap201696144027" width="1200" height="763" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696144027" name="imgmap201696144027"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Faustine Steinmetz - 6" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>SS17 COLLECTION INSPIRATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SNACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO OUTFIT:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>FAUSTINE STEINMETZ</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nParis, but I think of London\r\nas my home too.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSeven Sisters\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHummus and carrots but\r\nnormally I have crisps for\r\ndinner every night in the\r\nlead up to fashion week.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nA massive black sweatshirt\r\ndress, I’ve been wearing\r\nit every day for the last\r\ntwo years.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe light, which is very\r\nabstract and different for\r\nme. Think shadows, light and\r\nhow colour looks in different\r\ntypes of light.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDenim, but slightly twisted\r\nin a weird way.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nDefinitely Charlotte\r\nRampling. She’s so confident\r\nand I think that’s the sexiest\r\nthing about a woman.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nI got introduced to Karl\r\nLagerfeld and he already\r\nknew who I was, I couldn’t\r\nspeak for ages and then I\r\nhad to go and call my mum!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nThe Dazed playlist.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"DENIM, BUT SLIGHTLY TWISTED\r\nIN A WEIRD WAY."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-7" class="item item-7 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK7.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Ashley Williams - 7" usemap="#imgmap201696145953" width="1200" height="771" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696145953" name="imgmap201696145953"> <area title="" alt="Newgen SS17 Ashley Williams - 7" shape="default" nohref="nohref" /></map>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_1 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>HOMETOWN:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_2 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO LOCATION:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_3 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>CURRENTLY OBSESSED WITH:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_4 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WOULD YOU LOVE TO WEAR IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_5 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>FASHION IDOL:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_6 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>STUDIO SOUNDTRACK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_7 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>TRADEMARK LOOK:</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_8 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>BEST FASHION MOMENTS SO FAR?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_9 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h3>WHO WEARS IT?</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_10 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSharjah, United Arab Emirates\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_11 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nHackney\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_12 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nBras.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_13 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nGirls and boys everywhere.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_14 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nSofia Coppola.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_15 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nE.T\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_16 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\n‘R U Married?’ by Detroit\r\nin Effect.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_17 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nA teenage boy designing for\r\ngirls, with lots of graphics.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_18 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n\r\nAll of it!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_19 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h2>ASHLEY WILLIAMS</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imageMapBlock imageMapBlockItem_20 ">\r\n<div class="custom-html-content">\r\n<h4>"A TEENAGE BOY DESIGNING FOR\r\nGIRLS, WITH LOTS OF GRAPHICS."</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="item-120751-8" class="item item-8 isotope-item">\r\n<div class="imageMap"><img src="http://media.topshop.com/wcsstore/ConsumerDirectStorefrontAssetStore/images/colors/color7/cms/pages/static/static-0000120751/images/BLANK-8.jpg" alt="Newgen SS17 Paula Knorr - 8" usemap="#imgmap201696153743" width="1200" height="852" border="0" />\r\n<map id="imgmap201696153743" name="i